quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  51,47,"Kandi ikirere twacyubakanye imbaraga, ndetse dufite ubushobozi bwo kucyagura"
  51,48,N’isi twarayishashe; mbega ukuntu twayishashe neza
  51,49,"No muri buri kintu twaremyemo ikigabo n’ikigore, kugira ngo mwibuke (ubushobozi bwa Allah)"
  51,50,"Bityo, nimuhungire kwa Allah. Mu by’ukuri, njye (Muhamadi) ndi umuburizi wanyu ugaragara umuturutseho"
  51,51,"Kandi ntimuzabangikanye Allah n’ikigirwamana icyo aricyo cyose. Mu by’ukuri, njye (Muhamadi) ndi umuburizi wanyu ugaragara umuturutseho"
  51,52,"Ni nk’uko, nta ntumwa n’imwe yoherejwe ku babayeho mbere yabo ngo babure kuvuga bati \"Ni umurozi cyangwa umusazi"
  51,53,"Ese (imvugo nk’izi) barazihererekanyaga? (Oya, si uko bimeze), ahubwo bose bari abantu barengera (imbibi za Allah)"
  51,54,"Bityo, (yewe Muhamadi) birengagize kandi ntuzabigayirwa (kuko wamaze gusohoza ubutumwa)"
  51,55,"Unibutse kuko mu by’ukuri, urwibutso rugirira akamaro abemeramana"
  51,56,Kandi nta kindi naremeye amajini n’abantu bitari ukugira ngo bansenge
  51,57,"Simbakeneyeho amafunguro, ndetse nta n’ubwo mbakeneyeho ko bangaburira"
  51,58,"Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni we Utanga amafunguro, Nyirimbaraga, Ukomeye bihebuje"
  51,59,"Kandi rwose abakora ibibi bazagira umugabane (w’ibihano) umeze nk’umugabane bagenzi babo bababanjirije babonye; bityo, binsaba kwihutisha (kubahana)"
  51,60,Ibihano bikomeye bizaba kuri babandi bahakanye umunsi basezeranyijwe